reviews.reviewTitle: Compact power house for all your charging needs!
reviews.reviewText: I recently got my hands on the PowerPort III 20W Cube, and it has been an absolute game-changer for my charging routine. This compact yet powerful charger has quickly become an essential gadget in my daily life.One of the standout features of the PowerPort III 20W Cube is its blazing-fast charging capability. With 20W of power, it charges my devices at an impressive speed, saving me valuable time during busy days. Whether I need to charge my smartphone, tablet, or other gadgets, this little cube handles it all with ease.The design of the PowerPort III 20W Cube is both sleek and space-saving. Its compact size allows it to fit snugly in any outlet, without obstructing adjacent sockets. This feature is especially handy when traveling or using multiple devices in tight spaces.Another aspect I love about this charger is its versatility. Equipped with Power Delivery (PD) technology, it ensures optimal charging performance for a wide range of devices, including my IPhone 13, iPadPro and iPad 10th generation.Furthermore, the PowerPort III 20W Cube’s build quality feels robust and durable, giving me confidence that it will withstand the test of time and regular use. The solid construction also makes it a reliable travel companion, as I can trust it to perform consistently wherever I go.In conclusion, the PowerPort III 20W Cube has proven to be an outstanding charging solution that lives up to its promises. Its speedy charging, compact design, and broad compatibility make it a must-have accessory for anyone who relies heavily on their devices. Whether you’re at home, in the office, or on the go, this little powerhouse will keep your devices juiced up efficiently and safely. Highly recommended!

reviews.reviewTitle: This fast charger is small and the folding feature is a great plus point.
reviews.reviewText: Expensive but worthwhile. Very lightweight but sturdy. Ideal for travel

Is able to quickly charge my phone, and 20W is a good balance between speed and heat on the phone. Super fast charging isn't too necessary in my case as these are mainly for home use, and slower is better especially if charging overnight, and when travelling, I have a portable power bank. For the price of a two-pack, these are a great value for the Anker quality.Small size of the charger is great, it won't block other ports if plugged into a power bar. Extremely portable with the foldable prongs.

Anker's 20W USB C Charger has swiftly become my go-to charger. It's compact, foldable, and impressively fast. Its durable build, along with its budget-friendly price, adds even more value. Plus, it charges my S22 Ultra, OLED Switch, and S7+ Tablet with ease. A perfect fit for any room, it's a versatile charging solution that gets the job done efficiently.
Bought this for use with my iPhone 15 - it has worked well and is very portable. No issues to date and charges very quickly.
